{"title":"Bike Saddle Box program lets you demo any saddle on your own bike","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/09/bike-saddle-box-rental-program/","date":1628540791000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Sick of spending hours picking out a saddle that just ends up hurting your back or chafing your bits anyway? Then check out Bike Fit Box’s new Bike Saddle Box feature. The first-of-its-kind program lets you choose a few saddles to try and then sends them to your door for you to test on your own bike.</p><figure id=\"attachment_264689\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-264689\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x290/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" alt=\"2021 Mark Cavendish 3x Tour de France stage winning green sprinter jersey Specialized S-Works Tarmac SL7, S-Works Power Mirror saddle\" width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-297x178.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-800x480.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-120x72.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-768x461.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-696x418.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-1068x641.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-700x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x290/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" ezoid=\"0.9360375207993856\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-297x178.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-800x480.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-120x72.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-768x461.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-696x418.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-1068x641.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09100027/2021-Mark-Cavendish-3x-Tour-de-France-stage-winning-green-sprinter-jersey-Specialized-S-Works-Tarmac-SL7_Power-Mirro-saddle-700x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 700w\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-264689\">S-Works Power Mirror saddle</figcaption></figure><p>And it’s all relatively risk-free. You’re on the hook for a rental fee, and of course, damaged units are your responsibility. On the other hand, you’ll get a discounted rate if you decide to keep any of them.</p><p>“Cyclists can test ride these saddles at home on their own bike for as many rides as they like,” said <a href=\"https://bikefitbox.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bike Fit Box</a> Founder Brady Irwin. “[K]eep what you love, send back what you don’t. It’s that simple — and should always be this simple — to make your next ride more comfortable.”</p><h2>What You Get: Bike Saddle Box Terms</h2><p>Riders can cherry-pick from over 40 saddle choices with Bike Saddle Box. A wide range of fits, widths, and styles are available along a pricing scale up to the neighborhood of MSRP $300. Represented brands include <a href=\"https://us.selleitalia.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Selle Italia</a>, <a href=\"https://www.fizik.com/us_en/shop/saddles/road.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fitzik</a>, <a href=\"https://prologo.it/en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Prologo</a>, <a href=\"https://ismseat.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ISM</a>, <a href=\"https://www.origin8.bike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Origin8</a>, and more.</p><figure id=\"attachment_252651\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-252651\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail.jpg\" alt=\"Selle Italia Flite Boost Pro Team Kit Carbonio Superflow road saddle, rear detail\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08120837/Selle-Italia-Flite-Boost-Pro-Team-Kit-Carbonio-Superflow-road-saddle_detail-630x420.jpg 630w\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-252651\">The Selle Italia Flite Boost Pro (available through Bike Saddle Box)</figcaption></figure><p>To get started with the box program, choose at least two saddles from the product catalog. Then, select the rental option during checkout. The process lets you pick your dates, then determines a rate and <em>voilà —&nbsp;</em>a stable of test units appear at your door.</p><h2>Pricing Details</h2><p>Rental prices can vary depending on the saddle. For instance, the relatively rudimentary Origin8 Throne goes for $25, but the titanium-and-carbon Selle Italia SP-01 Boost Superflow rents for $75.</p><p>Either way, pricing is straightforward and no-nonsense. All you do is pick your units and your dates, load up your cart and wait.</p><p>At the moment, Bike Saddle Box gives you the best control over your <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/03/fair-bicycle-drop-best-reverb-offset-saddle-clamp-alters-setback-and-effective-seat-angle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">saddle spec</a>. Sure, you’ll need some extra coin for rental fees, but doesn’t it seem worth cutting out the hassle and/or return costs for gear that doesn’t work?</p><p><a href=\"https://bikefitbox.com/bikesaddlebox/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Check out its web page</a> for more details and full user terms.</p><figure id=\"attachment_267622\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-267622\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09105842/shutterstock_1102838001.jpg\" alt=\"adjusting bike saddle\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09105842/shutterstock_1102838001.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09105842/shutterstock_1102838001-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09105842/shutterstock_1102838001-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09105842/shutterstock_1102838001-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09105842/shutterstock_1102838001-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09105842/shutterstock_1102838001-1536x1024.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09105842/shutterstock_1102838001-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09105842/shutterstock_1102838001-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/09105842/shutterstock_1102838001-1920x1280.j